2019-04-09  Lauren Coombe   <lcoombe@bcgsc.ca>

	* Release version 1.0.3
	* Consider barcode sequence to be all non-white space characters after
	the "BX:Z" tag
	* Added arks-make Makefile for running ARKS pipeline
	* Add ARKS test demo
	* Correct default parameter value (-e)
	* makeTSVfile.py uses distance estimations for dist_category in TSV
	checkpoint file for LINKS
	* Change default gap size to 100bp (in makeTSVfile.py)

